item.description:
Free class at Whole Foods Market in Framingham.

The class will focus on substituting dairy products with healthier alternatives and there will be samples of vegan Five Layer Dip, Tofu Ricotta Stuffed Tomatoes and a variety of plant milks. 

Whole Foods' Healthy Eating Specialist will demonstrate how to make tofu based, nutrient-dense Migas Especiales from Engine 2 Diet cookbook.
item.name: Free Vegan Cooking Class Inspired by Engine 2 Diet
